00:16.680 --> 00:20.560
<font color="#ffffff">On the streets of Paris, I hear you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">call yourself...</font>

00:21.840 --> 00:22.880
<font color="#ffffff">..justice.</font>

00:31.080 --> 00:32.240
<font color="#ffffff">HE COUGHS</font>

00:34.920 --> 00:36.400
<font color="#ffffff">First, you steal our money.</font>

00:36.400 --> 00:38.440
<font color="#ffffff">Then, our loved ones.</font>

00:38.440 --> 00:40.080
<font color="#ffffff">Yet, they did no nothing to harm</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you.</font>

00:41.280 --> 00:42.320
<font color="#ffffff">Or the King.</font>

00:43.600 --> 00:44.640
<font color="#ffffff">So, today...</font>

00:46.720 --> 00:47.760
<font color="#ffffff">..I am justice.</font>

00:50.320 --> 00:51.960
<font color="#ffffff">HE GASPS</font>

00:53.320 --> 00:55.000
<font color="#ffffff">HE GROANS</font>

00:56.840 --> 01:00.680
<font color="#ffffff">A scar for every day the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">King keeps them imprisoned.</font>

01:00.680 --> 01:02.400
<font color="#ffffff">HE GASPS</font>

01:08.760 --> 01:10.040
<font color="#ffffff">HE EXHALES</font>

01:12.360 --> 01:18.040
<font color="#ffff00">Sire, Monsieur Marchal has many</font>
<font color="#ffff00">enemies and many of them would seek</font>

01:18.040 --> 01:19.480
<font color="#ffff00">the opportunity to do him harm.</font>

01:19.480 --> 01:21.760
<font color="#ffffff">No. He is not the target.</font>

01:22.960 --> 01:27.280
<font color="#ffffff">I am. This is a reprisal for the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">prisoners taken in Paris.</font>

01:27.280 --> 01:29.320
<font color="#ffffff">I have three options.</font>

01:29.320 --> 01:31.240
<font color="#ffffff">Execute the prisoners,</font>

01:31.240 --> 01:36.760
<font color="#ffffff">take Paris apart brick by brick</font>
<font color="#ffffff">until Fabien is located, or both.</font>

01:36.760 --> 01:40.960
<font color="#ffff00">If I may say, sire, both options</font>
<font color="#ffff00">seem excessive.</font>

01:40.960 --> 01:42.400
<font color="#ffffff">They almost killed you.</font>

01:42.400 --> 01:44.400
<font color="#ffffff">They've abducted of my head of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">security.</font>

01:44.400 --> 01:45.560
<font color="#ffffff">That is excessive!</font>

01:47.720 --> 01:50.520
<font color="#ffffff">Gather some men. Start at the place</font>
<font color="#ffffff">where we took the prisoners.</font>

01:50.520 --> 01:52.880
<font color="#ffffff">Knock on doors. Knock them down, if</font>
<font color="#ffffff">necessary.</font>

01:56.160 --> 01:59.840
<font color="#ffffff">How dare they? If it weren't for</font>
<font color="#ffffff">me, they would be living in squalor!</font>

02:01.080 --> 02:02.840
<font color="#ffffff">And where the hell is my brother?</font>

02:03.920 --> 02:05.800
<font color="#00ffff">I have no idea, sire.</font>

02:17.760 --> 02:19.600
<font color="#ffff00">No! No! No!</font>

02:34.000 --> 02:35.760
<font color="#ffffff">Brother, your absence has been</font>
<font color="#ffffff">noted.</font>

02:37.000 --> 02:39.520
<font color="#ffff00">I had important matters to attend</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to.</font>

02:39.520 --> 02:41.640
<font color="#ffffff">More important than a meeting of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">council?</font>

02:43.600 --> 02:46.080
<font color="#ffff00">I saw him. The man in the iron mask.</font>

02:47.120 --> 02:49.800
<font color="#ffff00">But before I could speak to him, I</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was attacked.</font>

02:49.800 --> 02:52.280
<font color="#ffffff">Who attacked you? </font><font color="#ffff00">The men who were</font>
<font color="#ffff00">guarding him,</font>

02:52.280 --> 02:54.960
<font color="#ffff00">but they're not just ordinary</font>
<font color="#ffff00">guards.</font>

02:54.960 --> 02:58.960
<font color="#ffff00">They are ready to kill and to die.</font>

02:58.960 --> 03:00.440
<font color="#ffffff">Did they know who you were?</font>

03:00.440 --> 03:03.040
<font color="#ffff00">There wasn't time for formal</font>
<font color="#ffff00">introductions.</font>

03:03.040 --> 03:05.040
<font color="#ffffff">So, what are you going to do?</font>

03:05.040 --> 03:09.520
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps I can help. In Monsieur</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Marchal's absence,</font>

03:09.520 --> 03:11.000
<font color="#00ffff">I could accompany His Highness to</font>

03:11.000 --> 03:12.800
<font color="#00ffff">the place where these events</font>
<font color="#00ffff">occurred,</font>

03:12.800 --> 03:14.760
<font color="#00ffff">and help him to unmask the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">attackers.</font>

03:16.480 --> 03:19.960
<font color="#ffffff">Brother? </font><font color="#ffff00">I wouldn't want to take you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">away from important business.</font>

03:19.960 --> 03:21.520
<font color="#00ffff">What could be more important than</font>

03:21.520 --> 03:23.360
<font color="#00ffff">ensuring His Highness's peace of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">mind?</font>

03:23.360 --> 03:25.880
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, forget my peace of mind.</font>

03:25.880 --> 03:27.840
<font color="#ffff00">I just want to know who tried to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">kill me.</font>

05:19.600 --> 05:20.840
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR CLOSES</font>

05:29.880 --> 05:32.720
<font color="#00ffff">It's a long time since anyone lived</font>
<font color="#00ffff">here, Your Highness.</font>

05:33.760 --> 05:36.480
<font color="#00ffff">Apart from poachers perhaps.</font>

05:36.480 --> 05:37.960
<font color="#00ffff">Or vagrants.</font>

05:37.960 --> 05:40.920
<font color="#ffff00">Never heard of a vagrant with an</font>
<font color="#ffff00">armed guard.</font>

05:40.920 --> 05:42.440
<font color="#00ffff">No, of course not.</font>

05:46.240 --> 05:48.080
<font color="#00ffff">And he was where when you saw him?</font>

05:49.120 --> 05:51.880
<font color="#ffff00">Here, where I'm standing now.</font>

05:51.880 --> 05:54.800
<font color="#ffff00">I saw him through... Well, that</font>
<font color="#ffff00">window there.</font>

06:12.320 --> 06:13.520
<font color="#00ffff">Shall we search outside?</font>

06:15.960 --> 06:17.080
<font color="#ffff00">Excellent idea.</font>

06:48.800 --> 06:51.280
<font color="#00ffff">I want you to visit all the houses</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in the area.</font>

06:51.280 --> 06:54.520
<font color="#00ffff">Question the inhabitants - have they</font>
<font color="#00ffff">seen anyone suspicious,</font>

06:54.520 --> 06:56.400
<font color="#00ffff">who does this house belong to,</font>

06:56.400 --> 06:58.680
<font color="#00ffff">and then go back to them by the end</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of the day.</font>

07:02.240 --> 07:05.400
<font color="#ffff00">I'm beginning to wonder whether I</font>
<font color="#ffff00">imagined the whole thing.</font>

07:05.400 --> 07:08.760
<font color="#00ffff">Your Highness, I believe that you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">saw someone.</font>

07:08.760 --> 07:09.800
<font color="#00ffff">The question is whom?</font>

07:10.800 --> 07:14.040
<font color="#00ffff">And I am as determined as you are to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">get to the bottom of it.</font>

07:14.040 --> 07:17.000
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you. May I suggest that we</font>
<font color="#ffff00">return to the palace?</font>

07:28.840 --> 07:29.880
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

07:32.760 --> 07:34.440
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty.</font>

07:44.800 --> 07:46.400
<font color="#ffff00">I thought you were on your way to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Spain.</font>

07:46.400 --> 07:48.440
<font color="#ffffff">I felt ill and decided to turn back.</font>

07:49.920 --> 07:52.000
<font color="#ffff00">Are you recovered? </font><font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

07:53.400 --> 07:56.960
<font color="#ffff00">Then, it's not too late. I shall</font>
<font color="#ffff00">arrange another carriage and</font>

07:56.960 --> 07:59.680
<font color="#ffff00">send word to the Emperor that you're</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your way. </font><font color="#ffffff">No.</font>

07:59.680 --> 08:02.800
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty, I urge you to leave.</font>

08:02.800 --> 08:05.560
<font color="#ffffff">My mind is set.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I realise my duty lies here.</font>

08:07.360 --> 08:11.760
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty, remaining here carries</font>
<font color="#ffff00">its own dangers.</font>

08:13.240 --> 08:14.280
<font color="#ffffff">You mean the King?</font>

08:16.760 --> 08:17.800
<font color="#ffffff">He shall not find out.</font>

08:20.680 --> 08:21.720
<font color="#ffff00">As you wish.</font>

08:26.360 --> 08:27.960
<font color="#ffffff">Have you received word from Leopold?</font>

08:31.040 --> 08:32.440
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

08:39.760 --> 08:41.440
<font color="#ffffff">COUGHING</font>

08:43.720 --> 08:45.240
<font color="#ffffff">COUGHING</font>

08:48.280 --> 08:49.800
<font color="#00ff00">Come now, you have to eat.</font>

08:52.680 --> 08:55.520
<font color="#ffffff">COUGHING</font>

08:59.480 --> 09:03.000
<font color="#ffffff">CHURCH BELLS</font>

09:32.480 --> 09:34.840
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, my God!</font>

09:34.840 --> 09:36.760
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GASPS</font>

09:38.720 --> 09:40.280
<font color="#ffff00">You know who that man is? </font><font color="#ffffff">Of course.</font>

09:40.280 --> 09:41.800
<font color="#ffffff">What the hell is he doing here?</font>

09:41.800 --> 09:43.480
<font color="#00ffff">I brought him.</font>

09:43.480 --> 09:46.200
<font color="#00ffff">Well, he took my son. </font><font color="#ffffff">And you think</font>
<font color="#ffffff">this will bring him back?</font>

09:46.200 --> 09:48.040
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah. </font><font color="#ffffff">You bloody fool!</font>

09:49.800 --> 09:52.520
<font color="#ffffff">The King's musketeers are already</font>
<font color="#ffffff">searching the city.</font>

09:52.520 --> 09:55.160
<font color="#ffffff">What if they find him here? He'll</font>
<font color="#ffffff">more likely get us all killed!</font>

09:55.160 --> 09:56.920
<font color="#00ffff">And what about Tristan?</font>

09:56.920 --> 09:58.680
<font color="#ffffff">Look, I am sorry for you.</font>

09:58.680 --> 10:01.280
<font color="#ffffff">And for him. But he cannot be my</font>
<font color="#ffffff">sole concern.</font>

10:01.280 --> 10:04.040
<font color="#00ffff">Yeah, what is your sole concern?</font>

10:04.040 --> 10:06.000
<font color="#00ffff">Buying favour with the King,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">perhaps? Eh?</font>

10:07.600 --> 10:08.640
<font color="#ffff00">My brother is right.</font>

10:10.320 --> 10:12.200
<font color="#ffff00">It was a stupid idea.</font>

10:12.200 --> 10:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">But our cause is not lost.</font>

10:15.440 --> 10:19.560
<font color="#ffff00">We must go straight to the palace</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and say that we have found him.</font>

10:19.560 --> 10:20.720
<font color="#00ffff">So, you'd betray me? </font><font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

10:22.400 --> 10:23.880
<font color="#ffff00">We refuse to give your name.</font>

10:23.880 --> 10:26.400
<font color="#ffff00">We say that we're here on your</font>

10:26.400 --> 10:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">behalf to negotiate an exchange of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">prisoners.</font>

10:31.760 --> 10:34.120
<font color="#ffffff">We?</font>

10:34.120 --> 10:35.480
<font color="#ffff00">You.</font>

10:43.560 --> 10:44.880
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR OPENS</font>

10:51.400 --> 10:53.280
<font color="#ffff00">I see Her Majesty's fully recovered.</font>

10:54.560 --> 10:55.960
<font color="#ffffff">You seem disappointed.</font>

10:57.680 --> 10:59.440
<font color="#ffff00">Only for you.</font>

10:59.440 --> 11:01.760
<font color="#ffff00">I know how much you wanted to see</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your brother.</font>

11:03.760 --> 11:07.080
<font color="#ffff00">What was ailing you? </font><font color="#ffffff">Just a slight</font>
<font color="#ffffff">chill.</font>

11:08.560 --> 11:11.160
<font color="#ffff00">If so slight, why did you not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">continue the journey?</font>

11:12.360 --> 11:15.040
<font color="#ffffff">I feared that with the travel,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">it would get worse.</font>

11:17.920 --> 11:20.800
<font color="#ffff00">I assume you've already made plans</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to leave again soon.</font>

11:20.800 --> 11:23.200
<font color="#ffffff">No, I decided to stay.</font>

11:23.200 --> 11:25.600
<font color="#ffff00">And your brother? </font><font color="#ffffff">Why all these</font>
<font color="#ffffff">questions?</font>

11:25.600 --> 11:27.640
<font color="#ffffff">His Majesty will drive me back to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the sickbed.</font>

11:27.640 --> 11:30.760
<font color="#ffff00">Well, since your brother is not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">expected to live long,</font>

11:30.760 --> 11:33.000
<font color="#ffff00">I merely assumed you would be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">determined to see him.</font>

11:34.720 --> 11:36.360
<font color="#ffffff">He no longer needs me.</font>

11:36.360 --> 11:38.600
<font color="#ffffff">A visit would have been for my</font>
<font color="#ffffff">benefit alone,</font>

11:38.600 --> 11:40.480
<font color="#ffffff">and I'm well used to denying myself.</font>

11:42.480 --> 11:45.840
<font color="#ffffff">Has Madame de Maintenon kept her</font>
<font color="#ffffff">silence since her departure?</font>

11:45.840 --> 11:47.240
<font color="#ffff00">I have not heard from her.</font>

11:47.240 --> 11:51.800
<font color="#ffff00">Nor do I wish to. </font><font color="#ffffff">Losing a close</font>
<font color="#ffffff">friend such as she can be difficult.</font>

11:53.040 --> 11:55.960
<font color="#ffff00">Unless the friend is not as loyal as</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you thought they were.</font>

12:14.960 --> 12:16.560
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you for accompanying me.</font>

12:17.560 --> 12:19.360
<font color="#00ffff">It was a pleasure and an honour.</font>

12:20.960 --> 12:24.320
<font color="#00ffff">I shall report back to His Highness</font>
<font color="#00ffff">as soon as my men have carried out</font>

12:24.320 --> 12:28.040
<font color="#00ffff">their investigation. </font><font color="#ffff00">No, I think we</font>
<font color="#ffff00">should call off the investigation.</font>

12:28.040 --> 12:29.720
<font color="#00ffff">Your Highness?</font>

12:29.720 --> 12:31.400
<font color="#ffff00">I have considered the matter and...</font>

12:32.840 --> 12:34.880
<font color="#ffff00">..I think my brother was right.</font>

12:34.880 --> 12:37.360
<font color="#ffff00">There are things more important than</font>

12:37.360 --> 12:39.960
<font color="#ffff00">a wild chase after a man in an iron</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mask.</font>

12:39.960 --> 12:41.200
<font color="#00ffff">As His Highness wishes.</font>

13:06.880 --> 13:08.240
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry this happened.</font>

13:09.800 --> 13:11.320
<font color="#00ffff">I do not blame you.</font>

13:13.560 --> 13:15.160
<font color="#00ffff">I'm grateful for your care.</font>

13:17.920 --> 13:20.320
<font color="#ffff00">How long have you served the King?</font>

13:20.320 --> 13:22.760
<font color="#00ffff">All my life. </font><font color="#ffff00">And does it not bother</font>

13:22.760 --> 13:25.760
<font color="#ffff00">you to just do exactly what the King</font>
<font color="#ffff00">says?</font>

13:25.760 --> 13:28.440
<font color="#00ffff">'Tis an honour to serve His Majesty.</font>

13:30.280 --> 13:32.440
<font color="#00ffff">My loyalty is recognised.</font>

13:34.400 --> 13:35.800
<font color="#ffff00">And is he loyal to you?</font>

13:37.120 --> 13:38.800
<font color="#00ffff">Of course.</font>

13:41.520 --> 13:42.560
<font color="#ffff00">But for how long?</font>

13:44.680 --> 13:48.440
<font color="#ffff00">He may dress you up in fine clothes,</font>

13:48.440 --> 13:51.560
<font color="#ffff00">but at the end of the day, you are</font>
<font color="#ffff00">no more than a useful tool,</font>

13:51.560 --> 13:54.240
<font color="#ffff00">and as soon as you have outlived</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your usefulness,</font>

13:54.240 --> 13:58.200
<font color="#ffff00">you will find yourself tossed into a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">common grave</font>

13:58.200 --> 14:00.160
<font color="#ffff00">just like the rest of us.</font>

14:03.480 --> 14:05.200
<font color="#ffff00">Do you know what it is to be poor?</font>

14:06.160 --> 14:09.320
<font color="#ffff00">To work from dawn till dusk</font>
<font color="#ffff00">every day?</font>

14:09.320 --> 14:10.680
<font color="#00ffff">I have seen poverty.</font>

14:12.400 --> 14:15.840
<font color="#00ffff">Suffering, horrors beyond your worst</font>
<font color="#00ffff">imagining.</font>

14:17.920 --> 14:20.120
<font color="#ffff00">And what about injustice?</font>

14:20.120 --> 14:24.320
<font color="#ffff00">It's all around you and you do</font>
<font color="#ffff00">nothing to stop it.</font>

14:24.320 --> 14:27.680
<font color="#00ffff">You're a fool. You should learn to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">curb your tongue.</font>

14:27.680 --> 14:31.360
<font color="#ffff00">And you should learn to open your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">eyes!</font>

14:32.840 --> 14:34.160
<font color="#00ffff">To what?</font>

14:35.720 --> 14:36.920
<font color="#ffff00">The truth.</font>

14:39.400 --> 14:40.880
<font color="#ffff00">I've been to Versailles.</font>

14:42.240 --> 14:48.400
<font color="#ffff00">I have seen the King and his court</font>
<font color="#ffff00">gorged on wealth and opulence.</font>

14:49.760 --> 14:52.280
<font color="#ffff00">Fat from wine and food.</font>

14:52.280 --> 14:55.520
<font color="#ffff00">Idle and gambling in debauchery.</font>

14:55.520 --> 14:57.080
<font color="#00ffff">That is the way of things.</font>

14:59.200 --> 15:01.760
<font color="#00ffff">We must all learn to accept our lot.</font>

15:01.760 --> 15:03.040
<font color="#ffff00">Must we?</font>

15:12.440 --> 15:16.840
<font color="#ffffff">You think you can dictate terms to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">me, to the King of France?</font>

15:16.840 --> 15:19.400
<font color="#ffffff">You dare tell me what to do?</font>

15:19.400 --> 15:21.040
<font color="#ffff00">Not I, sire.</font>

15:21.040 --> 15:23.000
<font color="#ffff00">The people who took Monsieur</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Marchal.</font>

15:23.000 --> 15:25.040
<font color="#ffffff">Give me their names.</font>

15:25.040 --> 15:27.680
<font color="#ffff00">I cannot, sire. </font><font color="#ffffff">Why not?</font>

15:27.680 --> 15:30.320
<font color="#ffff00">Because I do not know their names.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You expect me to believe you?</font>

15:30.320 --> 15:31.360
<font color="#00ffff">What's going on?</font>

15:32.440 --> 15:34.200
<font color="#ffffff">The people who took Marchal want to</font>

15:34.200 --> 15:37.160
<font color="#ffffff">exchange him for the prisoners we</font>
<font color="#ffffff">took. I want their names.</font>

15:37.160 --> 15:39.720
<font color="#ffffff">This fool says he doesn't know them!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You're wasting your time.</font>

15:40.760 --> 15:42.800
<font color="#00ffff">I know this man. If he says he</font>
<font color="#00ffff">doesn't know,</font>

15:42.800 --> 15:44.000
<font color="#00ffff">then it's the truth.</font>

15:48.320 --> 15:51.560
<font color="#00ffff">We thank you for your help.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I thank you for yours.</font>

15:54.520 --> 15:57.480
<font color="#00ffff">A straight exchange sounds like a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">reasonable solution to me.</font>

15:57.480 --> 16:00.520
<font color="#ffffff">You'd have them get away with this?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">If it saves Marchal's life, why not?</font>

16:00.520 --> 16:02.560
<font color="#ffffff">Because I am in no mood to be</font>
<font color="#ffffff">reasonable!</font>

16:02.560 --> 16:04.280
<font color="#00ffff">Your vision is blurred, brother.</font>

16:04.280 --> 16:07.240
<font color="#00ffff">Treat the people fairly, and they</font>
<font color="#00ffff">will treat you with respect.</font>

16:07.240 --> 16:11.280
<font color="#00ffff">Treat them with cruelty and excess,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and they will turn against you.</font>

16:11.280 --> 16:14.080
<font color="#00ffff">All that matters is getting Fabien</font>
<font color="#00ffff">back.</font>

16:16.120 --> 16:18.520
<font color="#00ffff">I shall supervise the exchange</font>
<font color="#00ffff">myself.</font>

16:20.560 --> 16:23.760
<font color="#ffffff">Very well. But he must be released</font>
<font color="#ffffff">first.</font>

16:23.760 --> 16:27.360
<font color="#ffffff">When I set eyes on him, then I shall</font>
<font color="#ffffff">release the prisoners.</font>

16:28.360 --> 16:29.400
<font color="#00ffff">Fair enough.</font>

16:36.120 --> 16:37.520
<font color="#ffffff">Duke.</font>

16:37.520 --> 16:39.040
<font color="#00ffff">Sire?</font>

16:39.040 --> 16:40.200
<font color="#ffffff">A word before you go.</font>

16:46.560 --> 16:48.240
<font color="#ffffff">Sorry.</font>

16:48.240 --> 16:50.040
<font color="#ffff00">You should never apologise for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">winning.</font>

16:52.680 --> 16:54.920
<font color="#ffff00">I had sensed you had your heart set</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on leaving.</font>

16:55.920 --> 16:58.640
<font color="#ffffff">I have now set my heart on staying.</font>

16:58.640 --> 16:59.720
<font color="#ffff00">What changed your mind?</font>

17:02.640 --> 17:05.280
<font color="#ffffff">Did the King ask you to speak with</font>
<font color="#ffffff">me?</font>

17:05.280 --> 17:06.960
<font color="#ffff00">Why would he do that?</font>

17:06.960 --> 17:10.720
<font color="#ffffff">Cos it's the sort of thing he does</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and because he knows we're close.</font>

17:13.000 --> 17:15.839
<font color="#ffffff">I played a spade, you just played a</font>
<font color="#ffffff">diamond.</font>

17:19.400 --> 17:21.880
<font color="#ffffff">Please confirm what I already told</font>
<font color="#ffffff">His Majesty.</font>

17:23.079 --> 17:25.800
<font color="#ffffff">I felt ill, I decided to return to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Versailles,</font>

17:25.800 --> 17:29.000
<font color="#ffffff">and I shall be staying here</font>
<font color="#ffffff">at His Majesty's side.</font>

17:29.000 --> 17:30.840
<font color="#ffff00">Are you asking me to lie for you?</font>

17:45.760 --> 17:47.320
<font color="#00ffff">Come on, everybody! This way!</font>

17:47.320 --> 17:49.200
<font color="#00ffff">Come on! Come on!</font>

17:49.200 --> 17:51.000
<font color="#00ffff">Let's go. Go, go, go!</font>

17:51.680 --> 17:53.200
<font color="#ffff00">Soldiers are back - run!</font>

18:06.400 --> 18:07.720
<font color="#ffffff">Fabien!</font>

18:14.000 --> 18:15.280
<font color="#ffff00">When do we get our men back?</font>

18:16.280 --> 18:19.640
<font color="#00ffff">Release him! </font><font color="#ffffff">No, no, no!</font>

18:25.320 --> 18:30.640
<font color="#ffffff">When Monsieur Marchal is safely in</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the King's presence,</font>

18:30.640 --> 18:32.480
<font color="#ffffff">your men will be freed.</font>

18:32.480 --> 18:33.560
<font color="#ffffff">You have the King's word.</font>

18:37.280 --> 18:38.920
<font color="#ffffff">You have the King's word.</font>

18:47.920 --> 18:50.000
<font color="#ffffff">Fabien, come to me.</font>

18:55.480 --> 18:57.600
<font color="#ffffff">You all right? </font><font color="#00ffff">Thank you, Your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Highness.</font>

19:00.560 --> 19:02.640
<font color="#00ffff">Fire!</font>

19:02.640 --> 19:04.080
<font color="#ffffff">No, no! Get back down!</font>

19:05.000 --> 19:06.440
<font color="#00ffff">Fire!</font>

19:09.160 --> 19:10.720
<font color="#00ffff">Fire!</font>

19:28.560 --> 19:31.520
<font color="#00ffff">I gave them your word!</font>

19:31.520 --> 19:33.440
<font color="#ffffff">I gave them a lesson.</font>

19:33.440 --> 19:35.080
<font color="#00ffff">And I'm sure they're grateful for it</font>

19:35.080 --> 19:37.760
<font color="#00ffff">now that you've slaughtered their</font>
<font color="#00ffff">fathers and brothers.</font>

19:37.760 --> 19:39.440
<font color="#ffffff">I did what was necessary.</font>

19:39.440 --> 19:43.000
<font color="#00ffff">Mindless slaughter is never</font>
<font color="#00ffff">necessary.</font>

19:53.080 --> 19:55.560
<font color="#ffffff">Monsieur Marchal, I'm pleased to see</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you've returned.</font>

19:56.720 --> 19:59.200
<font color="#ffffff">You must see a doctor immediately.</font>

19:59.200 --> 20:00.840
<font color="#00ffff">And the prisoners, sire?</font>

20:02.400 --> 20:03.600
<font color="#00ffff">What do you intend for them?</font>

20:05.240 --> 20:07.360
<font color="#00ffff">They will be treated with the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">respect they deserve.</font>

20:10.440 --> 20:11.680
<font color="#ffffff">Yes, sire.</font>

20:23.040 --> 20:25.000
<font color="#ffffff">COUGHING</font>

20:25.920 --> 20:28.800
<font color="#00ff00">It's all right. We'll be out of here</font>
<font color="#00ff00">soon.</font>

20:30.600 --> 20:32.400
<font color="#00ff00">Hey, friend?</font>

20:32.400 --> 20:35.600
<font color="#00ff00">The lad is sick. He needs a doctor.</font>

20:35.600 --> 20:37.720
<font color="#00ff00">If you do nothing, he'll die.</font>

20:37.720 --> 20:39.280
<font color="#00ff00">Is that what you want?</font>

20:39.280 --> 20:41.080
<font color="#ffffff">COUGHING</font>

20:43.120 --> 20:44.960
<font color="#00ff00">May you rot in hell.</font>

20:50.240 --> 20:51.480
<font color="#ffffff">You feeling better?</font>

20:54.120 --> 20:56.840
<font color="#00ffff">I am, Your Highness. Thank you.</font>

20:56.840 --> 20:59.120
<font color="#ffffff">What did they do to you?</font>

20:59.120 --> 21:00.920
<font color="#00ffff">Um, these things are best</font>
<font color="#00ffff">forgotten.</font>

21:03.120 --> 21:05.120
<font color="#ffffff">What can you tell me about these</font>
<font color="#ffffff">markings?</font>

21:13.040 --> 21:15.880
<font color="#00ffff">Mmm. I've never seen such a weapon.</font>

21:17.120 --> 21:18.440
<font color="#00ffff">"Diaboli mors."</font>

21:19.680 --> 21:21.360
<font color="#ffffff">Someone tried to gut me with it.</font>

21:24.080 --> 21:26.960
<font color="#ffffff">There is someone who might help us.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Are you fit enough to accompany me?</font>

21:26.960 --> 21:28.120
<font color="#00ffff">I am.</font>

21:34.840 --> 21:36.400
<font color="#ffff00">His Majesty called for me?</font>

21:42.280 --> 21:44.040
<font color="#ffffff">What is the Queen's mood?</font>

21:44.040 --> 21:47.040
<font color="#ffff00">Relieved that illness prevented her</font>
<font color="#ffff00">making the trip.</font>

21:47.040 --> 21:49.320
<font color="#ffffff">And you believe her?</font>

21:49.320 --> 21:50.560
<font color="#ffff00">If I may say so...</font>

21:52.240 --> 21:55.680
<font color="#ffff00">..His Majesty is unnecessarily</font>
<font color="#ffff00">suspicious.</font>

21:55.680 --> 21:59.400
<font color="#ffff00">No-one loves him more than his wife.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">She is above suspicion.</font>

21:59.400 --> 22:00.840
<font color="#ffffff">Your loyalty does you credit.</font>

22:02.440 --> 22:03.920
<font color="#ffff00">Sire, you need a distraction.</font>

22:05.080 --> 22:07.840
<font color="#ffffff">What sort of distraction did you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">have in mind?</font>

22:07.840 --> 22:10.240
<font color="#ffff00">There is an intriguing visitor to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the salons.</font>

22:10.240 --> 22:12.160
<font color="#ffff00">A scientist and philosopher.</font>

22:12.160 --> 22:14.000
<font color="#ffff00">Monsieur Dupuis is an entertainer.</font>

22:15.000 --> 22:18.320
<font color="#00ffff">I fear his ideas may not be to His</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Majesty's taste.</font>

22:19.640 --> 22:21.720
<font color="#00ffff">He is a Huguenot, sir.</font>

22:21.720 --> 22:23.320
<font color="#ffffff">An entertaining Protestant?</font>

22:26.760 --> 22:29.240
<font color="#ffffff">Let me share with you the human</font>
<font color="#ffffff">brain!</font>

22:29.240 --> 22:30.360
<font color="#ffffff">GASPING</font>

22:30.360 --> 22:32.600
<font color="#ffffff">God's finest work!</font>

22:32.600 --> 22:34.240
<font color="#ffffff">Capable of the highest art.</font>

22:35.720 --> 22:39.000
<font color="#ffffff">As a theologian, I bow to God's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Majesty.</font>

22:39.000 --> 22:40.600
<font color="#ffffff">But as a scientist,</font>

22:40.600 --> 22:47.560
<font color="#ffffff">I must investigate His creations for</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a true understanding of His genius.</font>

22:47.560 --> 22:51.400
<font color="#ffffff">Rene Descartes, himself a devout</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Catholic,</font>

22:51.400 --> 22:57.280
<font color="#ffffff">showed me that the seat of the human</font>
<font color="#ffffff">soul is located right here</font>

22:57.280 --> 22:59.280
<font color="#ffffff">in the pineal gland.</font>

22:59.280 --> 23:02.800
<font color="#ffffff">Through learning, we question, we</font>
<font color="#ffffff">marvel, we seek,</font>

23:02.800 --> 23:05.640
<font color="#ffffff">we come ever closer to finding</font>
<font color="#ffffff">answers</font>

23:05.640 --> 23:08.760
<font color="#ffffff">to the greatest questions of mortal</font>
<font color="#ffffff">life.</font>

23:08.760 --> 23:11.760
<font color="#ffffff">While God created the universe,</font>

23:11.760 --> 23:17.600
<font color="#ffffff">it is science that can uncover its</font>
<font color="#ffffff">secrets and mysteries.</font>

23:17.600 --> 23:20.320
<font color="#ffffff">APPLAUSE</font>

23:29.880 --> 23:31.480
<font color="#ffffff">It is a great honour, sire.</font>

23:34.160 --> 23:36.400
<font color="#ffff00">A fascinating discourse.</font>

23:36.400 --> 23:37.760
<font color="#ffff00">My congratulations.</font>

23:43.720 --> 23:45.000
<font color="#ffff00">Lock him up.</font>

23:48.280 --> 23:51.480
<font color="#ffffff">What is the meaning of this?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm a scientist!</font>

23:51.480 --> 23:54.040
<font color="#00ff00">I advise against it. It would be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">unwise.</font>

23:54.040 --> 23:55.240
<font color="#ffff00">I call it cowardly!</font>

23:56.400 --> 23:59.640
<font color="#00ff00">Leave it to with me. I shall speak</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with the King.</font>

23:59.640 --> 24:01.920
<font color="#00ff00">I'll see what I can do to ensure his</font>
<font color="#00ff00">release.</font>

24:03.160 --> 24:04.360
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

24:14.160 --> 24:16.360
<font color="#00ffff">Oh!</font>

24:16.360 --> 24:17.960
<font color="#ffffff">HE GROANS</font>

24:17.960 --> 24:19.000
<font color="#00ffff">Ah.</font>

24:20.760 --> 24:21.960
<font color="#ffffff">You lied to me.</font>

24:23.400 --> 24:27.560
<font color="#00ffff">I have no...idea what Your Highness</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is talking about.</font>

24:27.560 --> 24:30.560
<font color="#ffffff">The man with the mask of iron is</font>
<font color="#ffffff">still alive.</font>

24:32.080 --> 24:33.640
<font color="#00ffff">I'm governor of this prison.</font>

24:33.640 --> 24:37.360
<font color="#00ffff">I know every guard, every prisoner,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">every rat.</font>

24:37.360 --> 24:38.680
<font color="#ffffff">HE SPITS</font>

24:38.680 --> 24:42.360
<font color="#00ffff">If there was a prisoner wearing an</font>
<font color="#00ffff">iron mask, I would know about it.</font>

24:42.360 --> 24:44.320
<font color="#00ffff">Argh! Oof!</font>

24:44.880 --> 24:46.920
<font color="#ffffff">HE GROANS</font>

24:46.920 --> 24:48.120
<font color="#ffffff">Who is he?</font>

24:48.120 --> 24:50.920
<font color="#00ffff">How can I know who someone is if</font>
<font color="#00ffff">they don't exist?</font>

24:54.120 --> 24:55.360
<font color="#00ffff">Argh!</font>

24:56.400 --> 24:59.280
<font color="#ffffff">HE PANTS</font>

24:59.280 --> 25:01.840
<font color="#00ffff">I still don't know!</font>

25:01.840 --> 25:04.280
<font color="#ffffff">What about this? </font><font color="#00ffff">What about it?</font>

25:04.280 --> 25:05.560
<font color="#ffffff">Well, these markings.</font>

25:07.480 --> 25:12.240
<font color="#ffffff">What do they mean? </font><font color="#00ffff">I've no idea.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I've never seen such a knife.</font>

25:12.240 --> 25:16.840
<font color="#ffffff">You killed Marchal, didn't you?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">He killed himself.</font>

25:16.840 --> 25:18.560
<font color="#ffffff">On whose orders was he killed?</font>

25:20.880 --> 25:23.640
<font color="#00ffff">The only person who gives orders in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">here is me.</font>

25:24.760 --> 25:27.640
<font color="#00ffff">And since I didn't give the order to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">kill him,</font>

25:27.640 --> 25:29.680
<font color="#00ffff">he must have taken his own life!</font>

25:42.880 --> 25:45.000
<font color="#ffff00">I wondered whether I might speak</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with His Majesty.</font>

25:45.000 --> 25:47.560
<font color="#ffff00">It concerns the scientist</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Monsieur Dupuis.</font>

25:47.560 --> 25:49.080
<font color="#00ffff">A friend of yours? </font><font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

25:50.240 --> 25:52.680
<font color="#ffff00">But I believe he has been a victim</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of injustice.</font>

25:52.680 --> 25:54.520
<font color="#ffff00">Locking someone away for simply</font>

25:54.520 --> 25:57.000
<font color="#ffff00">stating his opinion seems to me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">excessive.</font>

25:57.000 --> 26:00.360
<font color="#00ffff">And this is what you wish to say to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">His Majesty?</font>

26:00.360 --> 26:02.200
<font color="#ffff00">I do.</font>

26:02.200 --> 26:06.560
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, I admit I did not expect to hear</font>
<font color="#00ffff">such words coming from your mouth.</font>

26:06.560 --> 26:08.960
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I shall take that as a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">compliment.</font>

26:08.960 --> 26:11.800
<font color="#00ffff">However, I warn you that the King is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in poor humour.</font>

26:11.800 --> 26:14.960
<font color="#00ffff">I strongly advise you to make your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">case once the clouds have lifted.</font>

26:22.920 --> 26:24.320
<font color="#ffffff">Yes?</font>

26:30.200 --> 26:34.720
<font color="#ffff00">I believe His Majesty has gone</font>
<font color="#ffff00">beyond the bounds of decency in his</font>

26:34.720 --> 26:36.600
<font color="#ffff00">treatment of the scientist Dupuis.</font>

26:39.080 --> 26:40.480
<font color="#ffffff">I agree.</font>

26:52.640 --> 26:56.760
<font color="#ffffff">GENERAL CHATTER</font>

26:56.760 --> 26:58.200
<font color="#00ff00">Look!</font>

26:58.200 --> 27:00.920
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHTER</font>

27:04.560 --> 27:06.280
<font color="#00ff00">You all right? </font><font color="#ffff00">Tristan!</font>

27:07.520 --> 27:08.760
<font color="#ffffff">INDISTINCT</font>

27:08.760 --> 27:10.280
<font color="#00ffff">Tristan!</font>

27:10.280 --> 27:12.080
<font color="#00ffff">You well, yeah?</font>

27:12.080 --> 27:14.120
<font color="#ffff00">Where is Olivier? </font><font color="#ffffff">I don't know.</font>

27:25.880 --> 27:27.200
<font color="#ffffff">Let him go!</font>

27:37.720 --> 27:39.440
<font color="#ffffff">SHRIEKING</font>

27:40.480 --> 27:42.440
<font color="#ffffff">SCREAMING</font>

27:44.280 --> 27:46.240
<font color="#ffffff">Argh!</font>

27:48.360 --> 27:51.160
<font color="#ffffff">Argh!</font>

27:56.520 --> 27:58.280
<font color="#ffffff">SHE GASPS</font>

27:58.280 --> 28:00.200
<font color="#ffffff">Find your power.</font>

28:01.760 --> 28:06.040
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SOBS</font>

28:36.000 --> 28:39.400
<font color="#ffffff">A one-armed beggar could do the job</font>
<font color="#ffffff">better. Get out of my sight!</font>

28:47.040 --> 28:48.080
<font color="#ffffff">Yes?</font>

28:49.160 --> 28:50.880
<font color="#00ffff">News from our spies in Spain, sire.</font>

28:52.920 --> 28:57.200
<font color="#ffffff">Continue. </font><font color="#00ffff">It concerns the cavalcade</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Austrian nobles spotted crossing</font>

28:57.200 --> 28:59.400
<font color="#00ffff">the border a few weeks ago.</font>

28:59.400 --> 29:01.640
<font color="#00ffff">It appears they've arrived in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Madrid,</font>

29:01.640 --> 29:04.000
<font color="#00ffff">and have been welcomed by King</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Charles.</font>

29:04.000 --> 29:07.160
<font color="#ffffff">I understood the King to be sick and</font>
<font color="#ffffff">dying in bed.</font>

29:08.280 --> 29:11.720
<font color="#00ffff">No, it seems he's in reasonable</font>
<font color="#00ffff">health and fully expected</font>

29:11.720 --> 29:13.040
<font color="#00ffff">to last the winter.</font>

29:19.080 --> 29:21.440
<font color="#ffffff">It would seem that the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">marriage is going ahead.</font>

29:24.240 --> 29:26.800
<font color="#ffffff">Arrange for Princess Eleanor to meet</font>
<font color="#ffffff">me in the gardens.</font>

29:39.560 --> 29:40.800
<font color="#00ff00">Senor Vasquez.</font>

29:46.480 --> 29:49.120
<font color="#ffffff">Madame. I have some good news.</font>

29:49.120 --> 29:50.160
<font color="#ffff00">Good.</font>

29:51.360 --> 29:53.960
<font color="#ffffff">The King has promised to consider</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the matter.</font>

29:55.760 --> 29:59.120
<font color="#ffffff">In the meantime, your dear Monsieur</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Dupuis will have to enjoy his cell a</font>

29:59.120 --> 30:01.800
<font color="#ffffff">while longer. </font><font color="#ffff00">I hope they don't</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mistreat him.</font>

30:01.800 --> 30:05.160
<font color="#ffffff">A man that fascinating? He'll have</font>
<font color="#ffffff">no trouble making friends.</font>

30:05.160 --> 30:06.600
<font color="#ffff00">True.</font>

30:08.760 --> 30:10.760
<font color="#ffffff">I know the King.</font>

30:10.760 --> 30:14.200
<font color="#ffffff">If he truly meant your friend harm,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">he would be dead by now.</font>

30:14.200 --> 30:16.320
<font color="#ffff00">I am grateful for your efforts to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">help him.</font>

30:17.800 --> 30:19.120
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't do it for him.</font>

30:20.680 --> 30:22.120
<font color="#ffff00">I know.</font>

30:24.760 --> 30:27.080
<font color="#00ffff">Are you enjoying your time</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at Versailles?</font>

30:27.080 --> 30:28.120
<font color="#ffff00">Very much.</font>

30:29.560 --> 30:31.200
<font color="#00ffff">You must miss home.</font>

30:31.200 --> 30:32.520
<font color="#ffff00">Not yet.</font>

30:34.440 --> 30:36.840
<font color="#00ffff">But you must be sad not to have gone</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to Spain as planned.</font>

30:39.760 --> 30:41.760
<font color="#00ffff">For the marriage. </font><font color="#ffff00">Sire?</font>

30:43.080 --> 30:46.240
<font color="#00ffff">I know of your uncle's plan.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You need hide nothing from me.</font>

30:46.240 --> 30:47.680
<font color="#ffff00">As you wish.</font>

30:50.040 --> 30:51.760
<font color="#00ffff">Your uncle will be disappointed.</font>

30:52.840 --> 30:54.840
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sure he will enjoy Spain without</font>
<font color="#ffff00">me.</font>

30:59.160 --> 31:01.760
<font color="#00ffff">What is it that pleases you the most</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at Versailles?</font>

31:01.760 --> 31:03.920
<font color="#00ffff">The gardens? </font><font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

31:03.920 --> 31:07.440
<font color="#ffff00">I prefer people to flowers.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Anyone in particular?</font>

31:08.880 --> 31:10.240
<font color="#ffff00">There is one.</font>

31:12.400 --> 31:14.480
<font color="#00ffff">I'm throwing a party this evening.</font>

31:14.480 --> 31:16.960
<font color="#00ffff">I hope to see you there. </font><font color="#ffff00">I would</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like that very much.</font>

31:18.240 --> 31:19.600
<font color="#00ffff">Good.</font>

31:27.400 --> 31:30.080
<font color="#00ffff">Tell the Queen I wish to see her.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Immediately.</font>

31:42.160 --> 31:44.320
<font color="#00ffff">I wanted your advice.</font>

31:44.320 --> 31:46.400
<font color="#ffff00">Of course.</font>

31:46.400 --> 31:49.440
<font color="#ffff00">On what subject? </font><font color="#00ffff">The subject of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">treachery.</font>

31:50.440 --> 31:52.360
<font color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

31:52.360 --> 31:56.120
<font color="#00ffff">I've recently discovered that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">someone very close to me</font>

31:56.120 --> 32:01.000
<font color="#00ffff">has plotted behind my back.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Not just to destroy me -</font>

32:01.000 --> 32:02.520
<font color="#00ffff">but to destroy my empire.</font>

32:04.400 --> 32:06.240
<font color="#00ffff">The question is what to do with</font>
<font color="#00ffff">them.</font>

32:09.440 --> 32:10.880
<font color="#00ffff">What would YOU do?</font>

32:12.000 --> 32:15.800
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know the circumstances. </font><font color="#00ffff">No.</font>

32:18.120 --> 32:20.760
<font color="#00ffff">But you do know the person involved.</font>

32:27.720 --> 32:31.400
<font color="#00ffff">Did you really think I wouldn't find</font>
<font color="#00ffff">out? </font><font color="#ffff00">What are you talking about?</font>

32:31.400 --> 32:34.520
<font color="#00ffff">You conspired with him to marry</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Eleanor to Charles, didn't you?</font>

32:34.520 --> 32:38.040
<font color="#ffff00">With whom? </font><font color="#00ffff">With dear cousin Leopold.</font>

32:38.040 --> 32:39.760
<font color="#ffff00">I knew of no such treachery.</font>

32:39.760 --> 32:41.880
<font color="#00ffff">That's why you were going to Spain,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">isn't it?</font>

32:41.880 --> 32:43.880
<font color="#ffff00">No, I wished to visit my brother.</font>

32:43.880 --> 32:46.880
<font color="#ffff00">As you know, he has a very weak</font>
<font color="#ffff00">constitution. </font><font color="#00ffff">Not that weak.</font>

32:48.760 --> 32:51.880
<font color="#00ffff">I've received confirmation that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">far from being at death's door,</font>

32:51.880 --> 32:53.400
<font color="#00ffff">your brother is in fine health.</font>

32:53.400 --> 32:55.640
<font color="#ffff00">If that's the case, then God's been</font>
<font color="#ffff00">merciful.</font>

32:55.640 --> 32:57.760
<font color="#00ffff">Explain to me the coincidence that</font>

32:57.760 --> 33:00.200
<font color="#00ffff">my wife and her cousin, both</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Habsburgs,</font>

33:00.200 --> 33:03.920
<font color="#00ffff">left Versailles within a few days of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">each other, both heading to Spain.</font>

33:05.880 --> 33:08.240
<font color="#00ffff">Explain it!</font>

33:15.040 --> 33:17.560
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, my God! You slept with him,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">didn't you?</font>

33:18.840 --> 33:20.560
<font color="#00ffff">Why did you come back?</font>

33:20.560 --> 33:25.000
<font color="#ffff00">I realised my place was by your</font>
<font color="#ffff00">side.</font>

33:25.000 --> 33:27.320
<font color="#00ffff">You mean, you couldn't go through</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with it?</font>

33:27.320 --> 33:32.120
<font color="#ffff00">You doubt my words, but I beg you to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">trust my actions, I came back.</font>

33:32.120 --> 33:33.160
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, you did.</font>

33:35.960 --> 33:38.080
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen shall be confined to the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">palace.</font>

33:40.680 --> 33:43.080
<font color="#00ffff">It's what we do to little birds that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">try to fly away.</font>

34:03.320 --> 34:09.760
<font color="#ffffff">BELL TOLLS</font>

34:15.520 --> 34:16.560
<font color="#ffff00">Mother Superior!</font>

34:18.360 --> 34:19.400
<font color="#ffff00">Please, sit.</font>

34:23.760 --> 34:25.080
<font color="#ffff00">This is a great honour.</font>

34:28.080 --> 34:31.080
<font color="#00ff00">I came to ask whether you are happy</font>
<font color="#00ff00">here.</font>

34:31.080 --> 34:34.760
<font color="#ffff00">Of course. I came here to seek</font>
<font color="#ffff00">redemption.</font>

34:34.760 --> 34:39.040
<font color="#ffff00">It is my wish to spend the rest of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my days in prayer and devotion.</font>

34:39.040 --> 34:40.080
<font color="#00ff00">Do not lie to me.</font>

34:41.239 --> 34:42.280
<font color="#ffff00">I am not.</font>

34:43.520 --> 34:47.480
<font color="#00ff00">That look of piety may fool many,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but it does not fool me.</font>

34:47.480 --> 34:49.840
<font color="#ffff00">You question my belief in God?</font>

34:49.840 --> 34:53.040
<font color="#00ff00">No. I question your belief in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">yourself.</font>

34:53.040 --> 34:54.760
<font color="#ffff00">I don't understand.</font>

34:56.639 --> 34:59.960
<font color="#00ff00">What will you do if the King comes</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to find you?</font>

35:02.480 --> 35:05.400
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know. </font><font color="#00ff00">I think you do.</font>

35:05.400 --> 35:07.200
<font color="#00ff00">But you're too scared to say it.</font>

35:07.200 --> 35:08.680
<font color="#00ff00">You want the King, don't you?</font>

35:08.680 --> 35:11.440
<font color="#ffff00">Yes. </font><font color="#00ff00">And?</font>

35:11.440 --> 35:12.480
<font color="#00ff00">What else?</font>

35:14.880 --> 35:18.720
<font color="#ffff00">That is all. </font><font color="#00ff00">No, it isn't.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Tell me the truth.</font>

35:18.720 --> 35:21.360
<font color="#ffff00">I am! </font><font color="#00ff00">You are not!</font>

35:21.360 --> 35:25.240
<font color="#00ff00">You are lying to yourself, to me and</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to God!</font>

35:25.240 --> 35:28.720
<font color="#ffff00">Stop attacking me!</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It is not me that is attacking you.</font>

35:28.720 --> 35:30.480
<font color="#00ff00">It is the shadow of doubt.</font>

35:31.680 --> 35:33.440
<font color="#00ff00">What do you really desire?</font>

35:34.960 --> 35:38.240
<font color="#00ff00">Say the word. </font><font color="#ffff00">Please, stop!</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Not until you say the word.</font>

35:38.240 --> 35:40.120
<font color="#ffff00">I cannot. </font><font color="#00ff00">Say it!</font>

35:40.120 --> 35:41.680
<font color="#ffff00">Power! I want power!</font>

35:43.160 --> 35:44.960
<font color="#ffff00">Dominion.</font>

35:44.960 --> 35:49.200
<font color="#ffff00">Joy, pain. I want to crush my</font>
<font color="#ffff00">enemies.</font>

35:49.200 --> 35:51.840
<font color="#ffff00">I want to feel the fire of our Lord</font>
<font color="#ffff00">inside me.</font>

36:08.200 --> 36:10.640
<font color="#ffffff">Welcome home, Bossuet.</font>

36:10.640 --> 36:12.920
<font color="#ffffff">I trust your travels were fruitful.</font>

36:12.920 --> 36:17.040
<font color="#00ffff">I bring greetings and good wishes</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from Cardinal Leto in the Vatican.</font>

36:17.040 --> 36:18.400
<font color="#ffffff">And a visitor, I see.</font>

36:18.400 --> 36:20.120
<font color="#00ffff">Monsignor Di Marco.</font>

36:20.120 --> 36:21.760
<font color="#00ffff">The Cardinal was kind enough to</font>

36:21.760 --> 36:24.160
<font color="#00ffff">provide me with a companion for the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">journey.</font>

36:26.080 --> 36:28.720
<font color="#ffffff">Please provide our esteemed guest</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with rooms and a meal.</font>

36:46.920 --> 36:51.200
<font color="#ffffff">When you say companion - in truth,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you mean spy.</font>

36:51.200 --> 36:54.120
<font color="#00ffff">The Cardinal insisted that he</font>
<font color="#00ffff">accompany me.</font>

36:54.120 --> 36:56.480
<font color="#ffffff">So, is Spain mine or not?</font>

36:56.480 --> 37:00.920
<font color="#00ffff">While the Cardinal acknowledges His</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Majesty's claim to Spain and its</font>

37:00.920 --> 37:02.920
<font color="#00ffff">territories... </font><font color="#ffffff">Yes?</font>

37:02.920 --> 37:07.640
<font color="#00ffff">..he also recognises the strength of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Leopold's claim.</font>

37:07.640 --> 37:11.120
<font color="#ffffff">So you've failed completely to win</font>
<font color="#ffffff">him round to our side?</font>

37:11.120 --> 37:14.800
<font color="#00ffff">I fear His Majesty underestimates</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the authority of the Vatican.</font>

37:16.000 --> 37:18.160
<font color="#00ffff">They will not be dictated to.</font>

37:18.160 --> 37:20.400
<font color="#00ffff">They take their own course in such</font>
<font color="#00ffff">matters.</font>

37:20.400 --> 37:21.440
<font color="#ffffff">You failed!</font>

37:22.480 --> 37:24.480
<font color="#00ffff">It is not I that failed, Sire.</font>

37:25.560 --> 37:27.440
<font color="#00ffff">I made your case as best I could.</font>

37:27.440 --> 37:30.800
<font color="#00ffff">The fact is your position is weak.</font>

37:30.800 --> 37:33.000
<font color="#ffffff">Is there no one I can count on in</font>
<font color="#ffffff">this court?</font>

37:38.080 --> 37:39.400
<font color="#00ff00">Come this way.</font>

37:53.080 --> 37:54.720
<font color="#00ff00">Wait!</font>

38:43.080 --> 38:45.560
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHTER</font>

38:50.440 --> 38:51.480
<font color="#ffffff">LAUGHTER</font>

38:54.280 --> 38:57.400
<font color="#ffff00">Ever since she left, he's been</font>
<font color="#ffff00">walking around like a corpse.</font>

38:58.560 --> 39:00.360
<font color="#00ffff">He misses her. </font><font color="#ffff00">I don't.</font>

39:01.760 --> 39:03.040
<font color="#00ffff">Neither do I.</font>

39:10.760 --> 39:13.720
<font color="#ffffff">Congratulations on the</font>
<font color="#ffffff">entertainment.</font>

39:13.720 --> 39:14.920
<font color="#00ffff">I serve to please.</font>

39:39.480 --> 39:42.640
<font color="#ffffff">Good evening. You look...</font>

39:42.640 --> 39:44.600
<font color="#ffffff">exquisite. </font><font color="#ffff00">Thank you, sire.</font>

39:47.040 --> 39:49.760
<font color="#ffff00">It must be wonderful being King.</font>

39:49.760 --> 39:53.000
<font color="#ffffff">How so? </font><font color="#ffff00">All that you desire is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">yours.</font>

39:53.000 --> 39:55.440
<font color="#ffffff">There are many things I desire which</font>
<font color="#ffffff">are not mine.</font>

39:55.440 --> 39:57.920
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps His Majesty needs to try a</font>
<font color="#ffff00">little harder.</font>

39:58.960 --> 40:00.680
<font color="#ffffff">That depends on the reward.</font>

40:20.440 --> 40:23.240
<font color="#00ffff">What the hell are you doing here?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I told you not to contact me.</font>

40:23.240 --> 40:27.960
<font color="#ffffff">I had no choice! The duc d'Orleans</font>
<font color="#ffffff">came to see me.</font>

40:27.960 --> 40:30.960
<font color="#ffffff">He knows too much. I've no wish to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">continue with this.</font>

40:31.960 --> 40:33.720
<font color="#00ffff">We are here to serve the King.</font>

40:34.800 --> 40:37.280
<font color="#00ffff">You should consider the consequences</font>

40:37.280 --> 40:39.960
<font color="#00ffff">if he finds out that you have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">doubted him.</font>

40:39.960 --> 40:43.400
<font color="#ffffff">Does the King even know what we're</font>
<font color="#ffffff">doing?</font>

40:43.400 --> 40:45.400
<font color="#00ffff">The King knows everything!</font>

40:45.400 --> 40:47.000
<font color="#ffffff">Then I wish to speak to him.</font>

40:47.000 --> 40:51.240
<font color="#ffffff">In person. I need reassurances.</font>

40:51.240 --> 40:54.680
<font color="#00ffff">That will not be necessary. As I</font>
<font color="#00ffff">said, His Majesty knows everything.</font>

40:55.800 --> 40:57.160
<font color="#ffffff">I think you're lying.</font>

40:58.400 --> 41:01.600
<font color="#00ffff">Unfortunately, you are never going</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to find out.</font>

41:01.600 --> 41:04.480
<font color="#ffffff">MUFFLED CRY</font>

41:04.480 --> 41:08.160
<font color="#ffffff">GASPING</font>

41:36.880 --> 41:38.120
<font color="#00ffff">Where are we going?</font>

41:39.240 --> 41:40.800
<font color="#ffff00">Somewhere private.</font>

41:45.320 --> 41:47.240
<font color="#ffff00">Scared?</font>

41:47.240 --> 41:48.600
<font color="#00ffff">Don't be ridiculous.</font>

41:50.440 --> 41:53.280
<font color="#ffff00">Tell me, what is it you like about</font>
<font color="#ffff00">me?</font>

41:55.360 --> 42:00.280
<font color="#00ffff">No doubt, you assume I was first</font>
<font color="#00ffff">attracted by your...</font>

42:00.280 --> 42:02.080
<font color="#ffff00">Wealth?</font>

42:02.080 --> 42:03.120
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

42:04.600 --> 42:05.960
<font color="#00ffff">But I have since come to know you.</font>

42:07.360 --> 42:08.840
<font color="#00ffff">And I find you beautiful.</font>

42:10.360 --> 42:11.640
<font color="#00ffff">Intelligent.</font>

42:12.760 --> 42:14.720
<font color="#00ffff">Witty.</font>

42:14.720 --> 42:17.080
<font color="#ffff00">Have you been intimate with a woman</font>
<font color="#ffff00">before?</font>

42:17.080 --> 42:18.560
<font color="#00ffff">Of course.</font>

42:18.560 --> 42:20.360
<font color="#00ffff">Many times.</font>

42:21.480 --> 42:22.720
<font color="#00ffff">Well, once.</font>

42:23.720 --> 42:25.000
<font color="#00ffff">Sort of.</font>

42:37.800 --> 42:40.720
<font color="#ffff00">What normally happens at this point</font>
<font color="#ffff00">when you're with a man?</font>

42:40.720 --> 42:42.000
<font color="#00ffff">Normally...</font>

42:43.240 --> 42:44.560
<font color="#00ffff">..one of us kneels down.</font>

43:12.680 --> 43:14.640
<font color="#ffffff">This is your first time, isn't it?</font>

43:17.400 --> 43:18.680
<font color="#ffff00">Is it so obvious?</font>

43:20.480 --> 43:23.360
<font color="#ffffff">Obvious. But utterly charming.</font>

43:28.480 --> 43:29.880
<font color="#ffffff">Let me see you.</font>

44:11.400 --> 44:12.440
<font color="#ffff00">Monsieur Marchal!</font>

44:14.080 --> 44:16.640
<font color="#ffff00">I heard about your terrible</font>
<font color="#ffff00">treatment.</font>

44:16.640 --> 44:19.320
<font color="#00ffff">I'm fine. The doctor stitched me.</font>

44:20.400 --> 44:22.560
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe you should consider a change</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in job.</font>

44:22.560 --> 44:24.960
<font color="#ffff00">Either that, or find somebody to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">look after you.</font>

44:30.880 --> 44:32.440
<font color="#00ffff">I don't like this game.</font>

44:33.600 --> 44:35.240
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not playing any games.</font>

44:48.200 --> 44:49.760
<font color="#ffffff">SHE EXHALES</font>

45:12.400 --> 45:13.840
<font color="#ffffff">Come here.</font>

45:20.400 --> 45:21.440
<font color="#ffffff">Closer.</font>

45:33.400 --> 45:34.720
<font color="#ffff00">May I ask a question?</font>

45:36.320 --> 45:38.480
<font color="#ffff00">Promise not to laugh. </font><font color="#ffffff">What is it?</font>

45:40.440 --> 45:41.720
<font color="#ffff00">Do you love me?</font>

45:45.080 --> 45:46.440
<font color="#ffff00">Did I say something wrong?</font>

45:48.840 --> 45:51.120
<font color="#ffffff">Er, no, the wrong is mine.</font>

45:51.120 --> 45:52.160
<font color="#ffffff">Get dressed.</font>

45:53.800 --> 45:55.840
<font color="#ffff00">I am not His Majesty's taste?</font>

45:55.840 --> 45:58.200
<font color="#ffffff">It's not your fault. Go back to your</font>
<font color="#ffffff">rooms.</font>

45:59.160 --> 46:01.800
<font color="#ffffff">You are just...a child.</font>

46:01.800 --> 46:03.600
<font color="#ffff00">But you can teach me.</font>

46:03.600 --> 46:05.480
<font color="#ffffff">Someone else shall have that honour.</font>

46:12.400 --> 46:13.640
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry.</font>

47:00.520 --> 47:01.920
<font color="#ffffff">Oh!</font>

47:04.320 --> 47:06.120
<font color="#ffffff">Are you all right? What happened?</font>

47:09.080 --> 47:10.840
<font color="#ffffff">You went with the King, didn't you?</font>

47:11.880 --> 47:13.880
<font color="#ffffff">What happened?</font>

47:13.880 --> 47:15.160
<font color="#ffff00">He said I was a child.</font>

47:17.880 --> 47:19.360
<font color="#ffff00">And I realise now he was right -</font>

47:19.360 --> 47:21.560
<font color="#ffff00">I'm just a child pretending to be an</font>
<font color="#ffff00">adult.</font>

47:27.080 --> 47:29.160
<font color="#ffff00">What were you doing? </font><font color="#ffffff">Come on.</font>

47:30.520 --> 47:32.280
<font color="#ffffff">Let's get you to your rooms.</font>

47:50.040 --> 47:51.280
<font color="#00ffff">You cannot sleep, sire?</font>

47:53.000 --> 47:55.320
<font color="#ffffff">My body is tired, but my mind is</font>
<font color="#ffffff">restless.</font>

48:02.080 --> 48:04.040
<font color="#00ffff">Can I fetch His Majesty anything?</font>

48:04.040 --> 48:06.000
<font color="#ffffff">Your companionship is all I care for</font>
<font color="#ffffff">right now.</font>

48:09.960 --> 48:11.240
<font color="#00ffff">May I speak my mind?</font>

48:11.240 --> 48:15.480
<font color="#ffffff">Yes. </font><font color="#00ffff">The young girls whose company</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you share...</font>

48:15.480 --> 48:17.120
<font color="#ffffff">What of them?</font>

48:17.120 --> 48:19.960
<font color="#00ffff">I fear they may not be the answer,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">sire.</font>

48:23.080 --> 48:25.120
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps the problem is another</font>
<font color="#00ffff">woman.</font>

48:28.040 --> 48:30.800
<font color="#00ffff">Not the ones you have. The one you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">have not.</font>

48:36.800 --> 48:39.120
<font color="#ffffff">She left of her own volition.</font>

48:39.120 --> 48:41.480
<font color="#ffffff">You said I was right to let her go.</font>

48:41.480 --> 48:43.520
<font color="#00ffff">We were both wrong.</font>

48:47.240 --> 48:49.760
<font color="#ffffff">If I go to her,</font>

48:49.760 --> 48:51.200
<font color="#ffffff">does that not show weakness?</font>

48:52.760 --> 48:54.320
<font color="#00ffff">On the contrary.</font>

49:18.440 --> 49:20.520
<font color="#ffff00">Holy Mary, mother of God, pray for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">our sinners now,</font>

49:20.520 --> 49:22.120
<font color="#ffff00">now and at the hour of our death.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Amen.</font>

49:22.120 --> 49:26.960
<font color="#ffffff">SHE CONTINUES TO PRAY</font>

49:29.520 --> 49:32.080
<font color="#ffff00">Holy Mary, mother of God, pray for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">our sinners now,</font>

49:32.080 --> 49:33.960
<font color="#ffff00">now and at the hour of our death.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Amen.</font>

49:33.960 --> 49:36.680
<font color="#ffffff">SHE CONTINUES TO PRAY</font>

49:38.000 --> 49:39.680
<font color="#ffffff">You told me I needed to change.</font>

49:41.760 --> 49:42.960
<font color="#ffffff">And I accept that now.</font>

49:45.800 --> 49:49.240
<font color="#ffffff">Without you, I am incomplete.</font>

49:51.160 --> 49:53.800
<font color="#ffffff">I sought solace in other women in</font>
<font color="#ffffff">indulgence,</font>

49:53.800 --> 49:55.400
<font color="#ffffff">but it was all empty ashes.</font>

49:58.160 --> 49:59.840
<font color="#ffffff">My judgement has been poor.</font>

50:01.800 --> 50:03.720
<font color="#ffffff">I need your counsel.</font>

50:07.080 --> 50:08.920
<font color="#ffffff">I want you back.</font>

50:08.920 --> 50:11.080
<font color="#ffffff">I don't care about who you once</font>
<font color="#ffffff">were.</font>

50:13.640 --> 50:14.680
<font color="#ffffff">I love you... </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh!</font>

50:16.320 --> 50:17.600
<font color="#ffffff">..for who you are now.</font>

50:35.080 --> 50:38.000
<font color="#ffffff">You will never kneel before me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">again.</font>

